ors.%20The%20letter%20was%20also%20signed%20by%2033%20other%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shareholders'%20requests%20%26quot%3Bto%20meet%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Director%20or%20management%20to%20discuss%20the%20company's%20plans%20for%20implementation%20of%20the%20proposal%20have%20been%20denied%2C%26quot%3B%20Gallagher%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Dollar%20General%20spokesperson%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20strong%2C%20ongoing%20shareholder%20engagement%20program%20and%20a%20well-documented%20track%20record%20of%20responsiveness%20to%20shareholder%20feedback.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDollar%20General%20has%20met%20with%20Domini%2C%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20multiple%20calls%20with%20members%20of%20executive%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDomini%20and%20other%20investors%20are%20asking%20Dollar%20General%20to%20complete%20the%20audit%20that%20shareholders%20approved%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDomini%20has%20been%20asking%20Dollar%20General%20about%20what%20it's%20doing%20to%20improve%20worker%20safety%20at%20its%20stores%20for%20over%20a%20year%2C%20Gallagher%20told%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20But%20the%20answers%20that%20it%20has%20gotten%20weren't%20satisfactory%20to%20the%20fund%2C%20she%20said%2C%20even%20as%20there%20were%20public%20signs%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20getting%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202017%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-paid-4-million-21-million-fines-owes-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDollar%20General%20has%20attracted%20millions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20fines%20from%20US%20Occupational%20Safety%20and%20Health%20Administration%2C%20or%20OSHA%2C%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20which%20it%20has%20actually%20paid.%20The%20issues%20that%20OSHA%20has%20found%20at%20the%20company's%20stores%20range%20from%20blocked%20emergency%20exits%20to%20an%20incident%20in%20North%20Dakota%20when%20Dollar%20General%20didn't%20give%20employees%20adequate%20protective%20equipment%20as%20they%20cleaned%20up%20a%20chemical%20spill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issues%20were%20so%20numerous%20that%20Dollar%20General%20earned%20the%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20violator%26quot%3B%20designation%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Labor%20in%20March%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F03%2F28%2Fbusiness%2Fdollar-general-osha-fines.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dollar%20General%20representatives%20that%20Domini%20met%20with%20were%20dismissive%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20violator%26quot%3B%20label%20in%20meetings%2C%20Gallagher%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20almost%20as%20if%20they%20felt%20that%20they%20didn't%20belong%20on%20the%20OSHA%20list%2C%20or%20that%20the%20scrutiny%20was%20misplaced%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomini's%20letter%20makes%20several%20recommendations%20to%20Dollar%20General%20for%20the%20audit.%20Among%20them%3A%20The%20retailer%20should%20pick%20an%20independent%20firm%20to%20conduct%20the%20audit%2C%20designate%20a%20board%20member%20to%20oversee%20it%2C%20%26quot%3Bfaciliate%20meaningful%20participation%20of%20employees%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20make%20its%20findings%20and%20next%20steps%20public%20once%20the%20audit%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20have%20shared%20with%20Domini%20and%20other%20shareholders%2C%20the%20Company%20plans%20to%20be%20responsive%20to%20the%20majority-supported%20shareholder%20request%20to%20'commission%20an%20independent%20third-party%20audit%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20company's%20policies%20and%20practices%20on%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20workers'%20and%20publish%20a%20report%20on%20our%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Dollar%20General%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Company%20has%20engaged%20a%20third-party%20with%20relevant%20expertise%20to%20conduct%20the%20audit%2C%20which%20is%20underway%2C%20with%20an%20expectation%20that%20the%20audit%20will%20be%20completed%20in%20sufficient%20time%20to%20publish%20a%20publicly%20available%20report%20prior%20to%20the%202024%20annual%20shareholders'%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson's%20statement%20continued.%20The%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20name%20the%20auditor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Dollar%20General%20doesn't%20make%20progress%20on%20the%20audit%2C%20Domini%20would%20consider%20supporting%20board%20candidates%20who%20want%20to%20make%20the%20audit%20a%20priority%20at%20the%20company's%202024%20annual%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we're%20voting%20on%20board%20members%20next%20year%2C%20we%20can%20think%20about%20'Have%20they%20met%20our%20expectations%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20supported%20the%20proposal%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDollar%20General's%20stores%20contain%20numerous%20hazards%20for%20workers%2C%20from%20blocked%20emergency%20exits%20to%20rodent%20infestations.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20has%20previously%20reported%20on%20safety%20hazards%20at%20the%20retailer's%20stores.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-stores-closing-fire-code-violations-too-much-stuff-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDollar%20General%20stores%20had%20aisles%20so%20cluttered%20with%20unpacked%20merchandise%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20were%20closed%20temporarily%20by%20fire%20marshals%20for%20blocking%20emergency%20exits%20and%20making%20it%20harder%20to%20evacuate%20in%20an%20emergency%2C%20Insider%20reported%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-rat-chewed-on-food-texas-dollar-general-store-2023-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOne%2520user%2520posted%2520a%2520video%2Ccontamination%252C%2520according%2520to%2520the%2520video.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDollar%20General%20in%20Texas%20had%20a%20rat%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20rodents%20chewing%20through%20bags%20of%20pet%20food%20and%20leaving%20fecal%20matter%20on%20the%20storage%20room.%20A%20local%20health%20inspector%20suspended%20the%20store's%20food%20permit%2C%20citing%20the%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20odor%20of%20decay%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20location%2C%20until%20management%20took%20care%20of%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffloirida-shooter-hated-black-people-swastika-painted-on-ar-15-2023-8%3F_gl%3D1*xok6i0*_ga*MTMyMjE5MjE0Ny4xNjk4MzIyOTg1*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5ODkzNDM3OC4zNS4xLjE2OTg5MzY0MDYuNDUuMC4w%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20Dollar%20General%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20two%20patrons%2C%20all%20black%2C%20were%20killed%20by%20a%20white%20gunman%20with%20a%20swastika%20on%20his%20firearm%20in%20Jacksonville%2C%20Florida.%20Domini's%20letter%20cites%20the%20killings%20as%20an%20example%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfrequent%20incidents%20of%20violence%26quot%3B%20at%20Dollar%20General's%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Dollar%20General's%20annual%20meeting%2C%20store%20employee%20David%20Williams%20cited%20rat%20infestations%20and%20threats%20of%20gun%20violence%20among%20the%20dangers%20he%20faced%20while%20working%20at%20one%20of%20the%20company's%20stores.%20Williams%20introduced%20Domini's%20resolution%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20fund%20during%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-takes-action-messy-overstocked-stores-marks-down-items-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDollar%20General%20is%20taking%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20inventory%20write-downs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sending%20special%20teams%20of%20employees%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20most%20merchandise-logged%20stores%2C%20executives%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20latest%20earnings%20call.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20direct%20efforts%20to%20improve%20safety%20for%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20action%20on%20safety%20at%20the%20chain's%20stores%20is%20a%20concern%20for%20many%20Dollar%20General%20shareholders%2C%20Gallagher%20told%20Insider.%20Many%20investors%20were%20persuaded%20to%20vote%20for%20an%20audit%20in%20light%20of%20the%20mounting%20citations%20from%20OSHA%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20financial%20risk%20that's%20associated%20with%20that%20is%20also%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20saw%20the%20state%20of%20worker%20safety%20as%20an%20impediment%20to%20Dollar%20General's%20growth%20plans.%20The%20retailer%20is%20close%20to%20opening%20its%2020%2C000th%20store%20and%20has%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmontana-store-puts-dollar-general-in-all-48-contiguous-states-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20location%20in%20each%20of%20the%2048%20contiguous%20states.%3C%2Fa%3E%20By%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20it%20plans%20to%20open%20990%20new%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-developer-sued-michigan-town-to-get-approval-store-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommunities%20are%20fighting%20Dollar%20General's%20planned%20stores%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20working%20conditions%20are%20among%20the%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20want%20to%20continue%20to%20grow%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20welcome%20in%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20Gallagher%20said%20of%20the%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20Dollar%20General%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20abitter%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-investor-no-progress-on-worker-safety-audit-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699016440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65427b0136d588dc55c80e80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-investor-no-progress-on-worker-safety-audit-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Domini%20Impact%20Investments%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Dollar%20General's%20board%20of%20directors%20after%20the%20dollar%20store%20repeatedly%20disregarded%20requests%20for%20updates%20on%20its%20worker%20safety%20audit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-investor-no-progress-on-worker-safety-audit-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Annual%20Report%20on%20Digital%20Labour%20Platforms%20Shows%20Worker%20Pay%20Is%20Largely%20Below%20Living%20Wage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F11165805%2FScreen-Shot-2019-09-11-at-4.57.43-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Zero%20of%20the%2012%20digital%20labour%20platforms%20evaluated%20in%20the%20Fairwork%20India%202023%20report%20showed%20evidence%20of%20providing%20their%20workers%20with%20a%20living%20wage.%20Only%20three%20of%20the%2012%20%E2%80%94%20bigbasket%2C%20Flipkart%20and%20Urban%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20ensured%20the%20local%20minimum%20wage%20after%20work-related%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20found%20no%20platform%20to%20ensure%20fair%20representation%20for%20their%20workers%2C%20meaning%20platforms%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20process%20through%20which%20workers%20could%20express%20their%20voices%20collectively%2C%20such%20as%20through%20recognised%20trade%20unions%20or%20collective%20bodies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRepresentation%20through%20a%20collective%20body%20or%20trade%20union%20is%20a%20vital%20dimension%20of%20fairness%20at%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fairwork%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20disconcerting%20that%20despite%20the%20rise%20in%20platform%20worker%20collectivisation%20across%20the%20country%2C%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20there%20was%20insufficient%20evidence%20from%20any%20platform%20that%20showed%20a%20willingness%20to%20recognise%20a%20collective%20body%20of%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFairwork%20evaluated%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20gig%20workers%20at%20Amazon%20Flex%2C%20bigbasket%2C%20BluSmart%2C%20Dunzo%2C%20Flipkart%2C%20Ola%2C%20Porter%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20Uber%2C%20Urban%20Company%2C%20Zepto%20and%20Zomato%20using%20five%20principles%3A%20fair%20pay%2C%20fair%20conditions%2C%20fair%20contracts%2C%20fair%20management%20and%20fair%20representation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20desk%20research%20and%20359%20worker%20interviews%20across%20Bengaluru%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Kochi%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20platforms%20were%20graded%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale.%20Under%20each%20principle%2C%20companies%20could%20receive%20two%20points.%20This%20year%2C%20no%20platform%20scored%20higher%20than%20six%20points.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20fair%20conditions%2C%2010%20platforms%20received%20the%20first%20point%20for%20%E2%80%9Cproviding%20adequate%20safety%20equipment%20and%20periodic%20safety%20training%20to%20their%20workers.%E2%80%9D%20A%20second%20point%20was%20given%20to%20five%20platforms%20for%20providing%20workers%20with%20accident%20insurance%20coverage%20at%20no%20additional%20cost%2C%20compensating%20workers%20for%20income%20lost%20due%20to%20medical%20leave%20and%20for%20ensuring%20that%20workers%E2%80%99%20standing%20was%20not%20negatively%20affected%20after%20returning%20to%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20fair%20contracts%2C%20seven%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20bigbasket%2C%20BluSmart%2C%20Dunzo%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20Urban%20Company%2C%20Zepto%20and%20Zomato%20%E2%80%94%20were%20awarded%20the%20first%20point%20for%20ensuring%20their%20contracts%20were%20accessible%20and%20comprehensible%2C%20and%20for%20having%20a%20protocol%20for%20data%20protection%20and%20management.%20Five%20met%20the%20requirements%20for%20the%20second%20point%20that%20required%20more%20transparent%20and%20clarifying%20language%20in%20worker%20contracts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20fair%20management%2C%20Amazon%20Flex%2C%20bigbasket%2C%20BluSmart%2C%20Flipkart%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20and%20Zomato%20were%20awarded%20the%20first%20point%20for%20providing%20due%20process%20in%20decisions%20affecting%20workers%20and%20maintaining%20channels%20for%20workers%20to%20appeal%20disciplinary%20actions.%20Only%20BluSmart%20and%20Swiggy%20received%20a%20second%20point%20for%20regulating%20external%20audits%20to%20check%20for%20biases%20in%20how%20work%20is%20allocated%20among%20workers%20and%20for%20adopting%20anti-discrimination%20policies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20year%2C%20the%20report%20focuses%20on%20a%20different%20theme.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20theme%20was%20discrimination%20and%20alienation%20felt%20by%20platform%20workers.%20Fairwork%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20provisions%20in%20place%20for%20fair%20representation%20and%20workers%E2%80%99%20inability%20to%20influence%20how%20platforms%20address%20collective%20issues%20has%20contributed%20to%20alienation%20or%20estrangement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFairwork%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20alienation%20is%20deeply%20intertwined%20with%20the%20discrimination%20that%20platform%20workers%20face%20due%20to%20social%20identities%20such%20as%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20religion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20a%20national%20scale%2C%20Fairwork%20said%202023%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmilestone%20year%20for%20platform%20workers%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20This%20year%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Platform%20Based%20Gig%20Workers%20(Registration%20and%20Welfare)%20Act%2C%202023%20was%20passed%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eregulates%20the%20engagement%20of%20platform-based%20gig%20workers%20and%20aims%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20social%20security%20and%20other%20benefits.%20The%20legislation%20came%20after%20years%20of%20platform%20workers%20organizing%20for%20their%20rights%20and%20raising%20claims%20with%20the%20State.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20rules%20for%20implementing%20the%20Rajasthan%20Act%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20framed%2C%20the%20act%20marks%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20providing%20social%20security%20to%20platform%20workers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fairwork%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Declaration%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20held%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20also%20called%20to%20ensure%20%E2%80%9Cadequate%20social%20protection%20and%20decent%20working%20conditions%20for%20gig%20and%20platform%20workers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20year%20that%20has%20seen%20the%20formulation%20of%20a%20significant%20regulation%20based%20on%20inputs%20from%20workers%2C%20we%20hope%20that%20highlighting%20the%20experiences%20of%20workers%20will%20point%20to%20the%20structural%20changes%20that%20platforms%2C%20consumers%20and%20the%20State%20alike%20will%20need%20to%20undertake%20if%20the%20platform%20economy%20is%20to%20offer%20its%20workers%20decent%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Professors%20Balaji%20Parthasarathy%20and%20Janaki%20Srinivasan%2C%20the%20principal%20investigators%20of%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20interviewing%20workers%2C%20the%20Fairwork%20India%202023%20report%20included%20a%20survey%20of%20963%20consumers%20across%20the%2012%20platforms%20to%20gauge%20consumer%20awareness%20of%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20platform%20workers.%20Fairwork%20said%20in%20the%20largest%20cities%20surveyed%2C%20there%20was%20significant%20support%20for%20bringing%20change%20to%20working%20conditions%20in%20the%20platform%20economy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CConsumers%20can%20use%20these%20scores%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions%20about%20which%20platforms%20to%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fairwork%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20scores%20can%20serve%20as%20additional%20resources%20for%20collective%20worker%20bodies%20when%20they%20raise%20demands.%20We%20also%20hope%20that%20the%20findings%20of%20this%20report%20will%20provide%20regulators%20with%20a%20basis%20to%20formulate%20policies%20for%20the%20platform%20economy%20in%20consultation%20with%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20workers%2C%20platforms%20and%20venture%20capitalists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699016437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F11165805%2FScreen-Shot-2019-09-11-at-4.57.43-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fannual-report-on-digital-labour-platforms-shows-worker-pay-is-largely-below-living-wage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fairwork%20India%20has%20released%20its%205th%20annual%20study%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20discrimination%20and%20alienation%20felt%20by%20platform%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fannual-report-on-digital-labour-platforms-shows-worker-pay-is-largely-below-living-wage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ABC%20News%E2%80%99%20Bob%20Woodruff%20Returns%20to%20Iraq%20in%20New%20Special%20%E2%80%98After%20the%20Blast%3A%20The%20Will%20to%20Survive%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699016400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGettyImages-1185575103.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1