20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2023%2F10%2F31%2Fsaudi-megadeal-normalization-israel-biden%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enegotiations%20on%20normalizing%20ties%20with%20Israel%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20White%20House%20said%2C%20but%20would%20likely%20demand%20concessions%20from%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20to%20restart%20the%20process.%20The%20UAE%20has%20reaffirmed%20its%20commitment%20to%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jns.org%2Fuae-official-abraham-accords-here-to-stay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20the%20Jewish%20News%20Syndicate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrly%20Goldschmidt%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20Israel's%20UK%20embassy%2C%20insisted%20that%20ties%20with%20Bahrain%20remained%20strong%2C%20despite%20its%20statement%20about%20withdrawing%20its%20ambassador.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20clarify%20that%20no%20notification%20or%20decision%20has%20been%20received%20from%20the%20government%20of%20Bahrain%20and%20the%20government%20of%20Israel%20to%20return%20the%20countries'%20ambassadors.%20The%20relations%20between%20Israel%20and%20Bahrain%20are%20stable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20longer%20Israel's%20campaign%20continues%2C%20and%20images%20and%20civilian%20deaths%20and%20devastation%20are%20broadcast%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20more%20public%20anger%20will%20build%2C%20putting%20huge%20pressure%20on%20Arab%20leaders%20to%20act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20danger%20Biden%20seems%20painfully%20aware%20of%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F02%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-administration-warning-israel-gaza-civilians%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20CNN%20reporting%20that%20US%20officials%20are%20cautioning%3C%2Fa%3E%20Israel%20over%20the%20repercussions%20of%20its%20attacks%20on%20Gaza%2C%20and%20cautioning