s%20take%20on%20the%20summit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SpaceX%20founder%20started%20out%20by%20thanking%20Sunak%20for%20hosting%20the%20conference%2C%20welcoming%20efforts%20from%20global%20leaders%20to%20confront%20the%20issues%20posed%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20actually%20it%20will%20go%20down%20in%20history%20as%20being%20very%20important.%20I%20think%20it's%20really%20quite%20profound.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20complimented%20Sunak%20for%20inviting%20China%2C%20calling%20its%20involvement%20in%20AI%20safety%20discussions%20%26quot%3Bessential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20them%20here%2C%20I%20think%20%5Bis%5D%20essential%20really.%20If%20they're%20not%20participants%2C%20it's%20pointless.%20I%20think%20if%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20UK%20and%20China%20are%20aligned%20on%20safety%2C%20that's%20all%20going%20to%20be%20a%20good%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EOn%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20thought%20AI%20would%20likely%20have%20a%20positive%20effect%2C%20but%20admitted%20there%20was%20sometimes%20too%20much%20optimism%20about%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20a%20future%20of%20abundance%20where%20there%20is%20no%20scarcity%20of%20goods%20and%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20somewhat%20of%20the%20magic%20genie%20problem%2C%20where%20if%20you%20have%20a%20magic%20genie%20that%20can%20grant%20all%20the%20wishes%2C%20usually%20those%20stories%20don't%20end%20well.%20Be%20careful%20what%20you%20wish%20for%2C%20including%20wishes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20a%20future%20where%20all%20children%20have%20access%20to%20an%20AI%20tutor%2C%20Musk%20also%20expressed%20hopes%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20help%20his%20son%20socially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20sons%20sort%20of%20has%20some%20learning%20disabilities%20and%20has%20trouble%20making%20friends%20actually.%20Well%2C%20an%20AI%20friend%20would%20actually%20be%20great%20for%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EOn%20government%20regulation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Tesla%20founder%20has%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-list-government-subsidies-tesla-billions-spacex-solarcity-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoken%20out%20against%20higher%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20rich%20and%20said%20he%20opposed%20government%20subsidies%2C%20Musk%20acknowledged%20the%20need%20for%20national%20leaders%20to%20play%20a%20role%20when%20public%20safety%20is%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20talking%20about%20digital%20super%20intelligence%2C%20which%20does%20pose%20a%20risk%20to%20the%20public%2C%20then%20there%20is%20a%20role%20for%20government%20to%20play%20to%20safeguard%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20it%20was%20a%20good%20idea%20for%20governments%20to%20act%20as%20AI%20referees%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bsportsmanlike%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we've%20learned%20over%20the%20years%20that%20having%20a%20referee%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20any%20sports%20game%2C%20there's%20always%20a%20referee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20balance%2C%20I%20think%20that%20the%20AI%20will%20be%20a%20forceful%20good%2C%20most%20likely%2C%20but%20the%20probability%20of%20it%20going%20bad%20is%20not%20zero%20per%20cent.%20So%20we%20just%20need%20to%20mitigate%20the%20downside%20potential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20future%20of%20jobs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20come%20a%20point%20when%20no%20job%20is%20needed%20%E2%80%93%20you%20can%20have%20a%20job%20if%20you%20want%20for%20personal