than%2020%20years.%20He%20handpicks%20the%20students%20for%20his%20class%2C%20and%20they%20virtually%20all%20score%20job%20offers%20from%20top-flight%20banks%20and%20hedge%20funds%20once%20they%20graduate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHanke%20has%20been%20a%20Johns%20Hopkins%20professor%20and%20currency%20and%20commodity%20trader%20for%20half%20a%20century.%20The%20veteran%20economist%20is%20a%20former%20adviser%20to%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan%2C%20and%20the%20ex-president%20of%20Toronto%20Trust%20Argentina%2C%20the%20world's%20best-performing%20mutual%20fund%20in%201995.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20signature%20class%2C%20students%20first%20learn%20to%20build%20discounted%20cashflow%20models%20from%20scratch%20using%20companies'%20annual%20and%20quarterly%20reports.%20Next%2C%20they're%20taught%20to%20run%20%26quot%3BMonte%20Carlo%26quot%3B%20simulations%20to%20generate%20potential%20scenarios%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20determine%20the%20likely%20price%20range%20for%20a%20company's%20stock%2C%20and%20gauge%20the%20probabilities%20of%20its%20shares%20rising%20or%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHanke's%20students%20also%20examine%20the%20market's%20expectations%20for%20a%20stock%20based%20on%20its%20current%20price%2C%20analyze%20companies'%20returns%20on%20capital%2C%20and%20critique%20how%20their%20bosses%20are%20paid.%20They%20consider%20everything%20from%20capital%20allocation%20and%20debt%20levels%20to%20stock%20issuance%2C%20dealmaking%2C%20and%20shareholder%20returns.%20They%20refine%20their%20models%20over%20several%20weeks%20based%20on%20feedback%20and%20further%20research%2C%20and%20have%20to%20defend%20an%20investment%20thesis%20to%20the%20class%2C%20helping%20prepare%20them%20to%20work%20as%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fbrk-b-stock%5C%22%3EBerkshire%20Hathaway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20takes%20a%20similar%20approach%20to%20valuing%20a%20business.%20He%20pores%20over%20its%20financials%2C%20tries%20to%20predict%20what%20it%20will%20look%20like%20in%2010%20years'%20time%2C%20and%20judges%20the%20quality%20and%20compensation%20of%20its%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20follows%20very%20much%20in%20the%20Buffett%20line%20of%20thinking%20about%20investing%20in%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Hanke%20told%20Insider%20about%20his%20course.%20He%20described%20building%20a%20cash%20flow%20model%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20Buffett-ish%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bclear%20to%20me%20that%20Buffett%20goes%20through%20the%20same%20type%20of%20Monte%20Carlo%20simulation%20in%20his%20head.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20looms%20large%20in%20the%20suggested%20reading%20list%20for%20Hanke's%20course%20too.%20It%20includes%20%26quot%3BPoor%20Charlie's%20Almanack%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20collection%20of%20wisdom%20from%20Buffett's%20business%20partner%2C%20Charlie%20Munger%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Intelligent%20Investor%26quot%3B%20by%20Benjamin%20Graham%2C%20Buffett's%20late%20professor%20and%20mentor.%20It%20also%20features%20a%20recommendation%20for%20students%20to%20read%20Buffett's%20partnership%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224351%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steve%20Hanke%20Johns%20Hopkins%20finance%20class%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F554d2a1a69bedd5f78073780%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222175%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProfessor%20Steve%20Hanke.%3Cp%3EPortia%20Crowe%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHanke%20makes%20a%20point%20of%20sharing%20many%20of%20Buffett's%20key%20teachings%20with%20his%20students.%20In%20an%20email%20to%20Insider%2C%20he%20listed%20several%20of%20the%20investing%20icon's%20lessons%20based%20on%20%26quot%3BWarren%20Buffett%20Speaks%3A%20Wit%20and%20Wisdom%20from%20the%20World's%20Greatest%20Investor%26quot%3B%20by%20Janet%20Lowe%2C%20and%20voiced%20his%20views%20on%20them.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20ones%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E1.%20%3Cstrong%3EBe%20smart%20about%20allocating%20capital%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20put%20great%20stress%20on%20how%20students%20should%20analyze%20the%20decisions%20surrounding%20the%20allocation%20of%20capital.%20That's%20the%20name%20of%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2.%20%3Cstrong%3EListen%20for%20opportunity's%20call%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Mr.%20Market%20throws%20up%20a%20price%20well%20below%20a%20firm's%20intrinsic%20value%2C%20pounce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3.%20%3Cstrong%3EEarnings%2C%20earnings%20earnings%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20add%3A%20Free%20cash%20flow%2C%20free%20cash%20flow%2C%20free%20cash%20flow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20%3Cstrong%3EAvoid%20risk%2C%20don't%20gamble%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20I%20link%20Monte%20Carlo%20simulations%20to%20my%20discounted%20free%20cashflow%20models.%20It%20allows%20you%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20probabilities%20and%20to%20stack%20the%20odds%20in%20your%20favor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%3Cstrong%3EAvoid%20excessive%20debt%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20nothing%20more%20important%20than%20a%20sound%20balance%20sheet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%3Cstrong%3EBe%20patient%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20learned%20to%20wait%20a%20very%20long%20time%20to%20make%20a%20move%2C%20often%20years.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E7.%20%3Cstrong%3EBe%20wary%20of%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3B95%25%20of%20what%20Wall%20Street's%20chattering%20class%20has%20to%20say%20is%20either%20wrong%20or%20irrelevant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E8.%20%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20sweat%20the%20math%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BForget%20the%20complicated%20algorithms.%20Learn%20how%20to%20read%20balance%20sheets%20and%20annual%20reports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E9.%20%3Cstrong%3EAdmire%20frugality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%