vements%20of%20the%20NDA%20government%20during%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20Yatra%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENovember%2020%2C%202023%20to%20January%2025%2C%202024.%20The%20yatra%20would%20traverse%20765%20districts%20in%20the%20country%2C%20covering%202.69%20lakh%20gram%20panchayats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20on%20October%206%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20(MoD)%20had%20subpoenaed%20the%20armed%20forces%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefence-ministry-selfie-points-narendra-modi%5C%22%3Epromote%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20in%20various%20fields.%20As%20per%20the%20directions%20issued%2C%20the%20armed%20forces%20will%20create%20822%20geo-tagged%20%E2%80%98selfie%20points%E2%80%99%20in%20public%20places%20across%20the%20country%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%20good%20works%20done%20in%20defence%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20%E2%80%9Cenables%20the%20people%20to%20get%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20initiative.%E2%80%9D%20The%20additional%20director%20general%20(media%20and%20communications)%2C%20MoD%20issued%20a%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20(SOP)%20which%20recommends%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20%E2%80%98selfie%20points%E2%80%99%20may%20contain%20a%20giant-sized%20picture%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%E2%80%9D%20Another%20order%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20MoD%20on%20October%209%2C%202023%20instructing%20soldiers%20on%20annual%20leave%20to%20promote%20government%20schemes%2C%20designating%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Csoldier-ambassadors.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13164820%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-4.46.40.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13164820%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-4.46.40.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13164820%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-4.46.40-300x143.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13164820%2FScreenshot-2023-10-13-at-4.46.40-1024x488.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679966%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22572%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20collage%20of%20the%20visual%20aids%20offered%20by%20the%20defence%20ministry%20to%20organisations%20and%20departments%20under%20it%2C%20to%20illustrate%20how%20the%20selfie%20points%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20extraordinary%20commandeering%20of%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20armed%20forces%20for%20propaganda%20at%20one%20go%20is%20obviously%20aimed%20at%20creating%20a%20positive%20public%20perception%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20general%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20particular%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20general%20elections%20to%20parliament%2C%20due%20in%20April-May%2C%202024.%20Looked%20at%20from%20several%20dimensions%2C%20this%20is%20a%20dangerous%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%20is%20the%20federal%20dimension.%20Article%201%20of%20the%20constitution%20says%20%E2%80%98India%2C%20that%20is%20Bharat%2C%20shall%20be%20a%20Union%20of%20States.%E2%80%9D%20The%20core%20objective%20of%20the%20constitution%20was%20to%20ensure%20national%20unity%20and%20integrity%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20performing%20the%20task%20of%20socio-economic%20reconstruction%20through%20democratic%20means.%20To%20achieve%20this%20purpose%20and%20to%20meet%20the%20special%20needs%20of%20India%2C%20the%20constitution%20framers%20developed%20a%20%3Cem%3Esui%20generis%3C%2Fem%3E%20variation%20of%20federation.%20The%20constitution%20incorporates%20federal%20features%20such%20as%20the%20distribution%20of%20powers%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20States%3A%2097%20matters%20are%20on%20the%20Union%20List%3B%20States%20have%20exclusive%20powers%20on%2066%20matters%20contained%20in%20the%20State%20List%3B%20and%20the%20Concurrent%20List%20consists%20of%2047%20items.%20The%20constitution%20envisages%20India%E2%80%99s%20governance%20as%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments.%20But%20of%20late%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20launched%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20federal%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution%20by%20attempting%20to%20capture%20areas%20and%20subjects%20which%20are%20within%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20states.%20This%20commandeering%20of%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20armed%20forces%20to%20trumpet%20the%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20directly%20to%20the%20people%20would%20further%20worsen%20the%20situation%20and%20accelerate%20Centre-state%20tension%20and%20friction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%20is%20the%20code%20of%20conduct.%20Under%20Rule%205(1)%20of%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Conduct%20Rules%2C%201964%2C%20no%20government%20servant%20shall%20take%20part%20in%2C%20subscribe%20to%2C%20aid%20of%20or%20assist%20in%20any%20other%20manner%2C%20any%20political%20movement%20or%20activity.%20Engaging%20members%20of%20any%20of%20the%20central%20civil%20services%20in%20the%20Rath%20Prabhari%20campaign%2C%20which%20is%20clearly%20political%20in%20nature%2C%20would%20therefore%20infringe%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Conduct%20Rules.%20%E2%80%9CRath%20Prabhari%E2%80%9D%20itself%20is%20a%20political%20(mainly%20BJP)%20parlance%20and%20not%20that%20of%20civil%20service.%20Considering%20that%20the%20idea%20underlying%20this%20campaign%20exclusively%20revolves%20around%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20past%20nine%20years%2C%20inevitably%2C%20it%20has%20a%20political%20connotation%20that%20cannot%20be%20wished%20away.%20Had%20the%20campaign%20covered%20the%20entire%20post-independence%20period%20as%20we%20celebrate%20the%20Diamond%20Jubilee%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20different%20proposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-servants-rath-prabharis-km-chandrasekhar-interview%5C%22%3EIt%20Is%20Not%20Civil%20Servants%E2%80%99%20Job%20to%20%E2%80%98Showcase%E2%80%99%20Govt%20Achievements%3A%20Former%20Cabinet%20Secretary%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20third%20dimension%20is%20the%20grave%20impropriety%20of%20it%20all.%20Civil%20servants%20and%20soldiers%20are%20not%20BJP%20cadres.%20Just%20as%20there%20is%20separation%20of%20powers%20between%20the%20judiciary%2C%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20legislature%20in%20the%20constitutional%20scheme%2C%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20line%20of%20separation%20between%20governments%20that%20come%20and%20go%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20and%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20which%20is%20permanent.%20The%20bureaucracy%E2%80%99s%20role%20is%20to%20conceive%2C%20design%2C%20plan%2C%20implement%20and%20supervise%20policies%20and%20programmes%20of%20a%20government.%20Its%20job%20is%20not%20to%20do%20propaganda%20for%20the%20same%2C%20since%20another%20government%20voted%20in%20by%20the%20people%20has%20the%20right%20to%20change%20the%20policies%20and%20programmes%20of%20one%20government.%20The%20%E2%80%98Rath%20Prabhari%E2%80%99%20programme%20envisaged%20by%20the%20present%20government%20is%20clearly%20a%20political%20programme%20intended%20to%20publicise%20its%20claimed%20achievements%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%20This%20amounts%20to%20misusing%20government%20machinery%20for%20election%20purposes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fourth%20dimension%20is%20the%20core%20electoral%20code%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20which%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20has%20directed%20the%20government%20not%20to%20conduct%20the%20campaign%20in%20the%20states%20(Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Chattisgarh%20and%20Mizoram)%20where%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20has%20come%20into%20effect%20due%20to%20assembly%20elections.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20ECI%20has%20no%20problem%20with%20government%20servants%20openly%20participating%20in%20this%20political%20propaganda%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20parliament%20elections%20in%202024.%20This%20is%20a%20grave%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20by%20the%20ECI.%20The%20commission%20should%20have%20stopped%20this%20serious%20distortion%20of%20the%20electoral%20code%20and%20level%20playing%20field%20by%20invoking%20its%20plenipotentiary%20powers%20and%20the%20far-reaching%20judgment%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1831036%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMohinder%20Singh%20Gill%20vs%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1978)%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20but%20where%20such%20law%20is%20silent%2C%20Article%20324%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20a%20reservoir%20of%20power%20to%20act%20for%20the%20avowed%20purpose%20of%20not%20divorced%20from%2C%20pushing%20forward%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20election%20with%20expedition%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20and%20fair%20election%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoliticisation%20of%20armed%20forces%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20coming%20to%20the%20brazen%20politicisation%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98selfie%20points%E2%80%99%20that%20have%20already%20come%20up%20in%20some%20places.%20The%20SOP%20lays%20down%20the%20themes%20based%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20catchphrases%20including%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%2C%20Sashaktikaran%2C%20Nari%20Shakti%2C%20digitisation%20etc.%20Look%20at%20the%20tearing%20hurry%20of%20the%20MoD%20to%20execute%20the%20scheme.%20Directions%20were%20given%20on%20October%206%2C%20execution%20to%20commence%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%E2%80%9D%20and%20action%20taken%20report%20to%20be%20submitted%20by%20October%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20the%20execution%20of%20a%20routine%20scheme%20or%20%E2%80%98all-hands-on-deck%E2%80%99%20to%20identify%20national%20defence%2C%20particularly%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20with%20the%20political%20party%20in%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Ftiming-of-mods-modi-selfie-points-is-alarming-military-must-not-become-a-political-tool%2F1819305%2F%5C%22%3Easks%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20distinguished%20soldier%20Lt%20Gen%20H.S.%20Panag%20(Retd)!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20move%20by%20the%20government%20violates%20Rule%2020%20(1)%20of%20Army%20Rules%20(1954)%2C%20which%20says%20that%20no%20person%20subject%20to%20the%20Army%20Act%20shall%20take%20part%20in%20any%20activity%20held%20for%20political%20purposes.%20Also%2C%20the%20SOP%20suggesting%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98selfie%20points%E2%80%99%20may%20contain%20a%20giant-sized%20picture%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20questionable%20because%20as%20per%20Article%2053(2)%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20the%20supreme%20command%20of%20the%20defence%20forces%20of%20the%20Union%20shall%20be%20vested%20in%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Republic%2C%20not%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F22121154%2F27368739091_b8ef73115b_k.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F22121154%2F27368739091_b8ef73115b_k.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F22121154%2F27368739091_b8ef73115b_k-300x148.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F22121154%2F27368739091_b8ef73115b_k-1024x504.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-620691%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22591%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20Photo%3A%20Public.Resource.Org%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20former%20Chief%20of%20Naval%20Staff%20was%20emphatic%20when%20he%20said%20that%20this%20programme%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20never%E2%80%9D%20have%20been%20contemplated%20and%20would%20have%20a%20negative%20long-term%20impact%20on%20the%20forces.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Ftiming-of-mods-modi-selfie-points-is-alarming-military-must-not-become-a-political-tool%2F1819305%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20quite%20clear%20about%20the%20concept%20underpinning%20the%20%E2%80%9Cselfie%20points%E2%80%9D%20programme%2C%20but%20with%20the%20general%20election%20looming%2C%20any%20endeavour%20which%20even%20remotely%20involves%20the%20armed%20forces%20with%20political%20influencing%2C%20can%20only%20ring%20alarm%20bells.%20The%20MoD%20should%20never%20have%20contemplated%20this%2C%20and%20one%20hopes%20the%20military%20leadership%20will%20explain%20the%20deleterious%20long-term%20impact%20of%20politics%20on%20the%20morale%20%26amp%3B%20cohesion%20of%20our%20professional%20forces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20else%20can%20one%20expect%20from%20a%20political%20dispensation%20hungry%20for%20power%2C%20and%20whose%20top%20leader%20in%202019%20described%20the%20Indian%20Army%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EModiji%20ki%20sena%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20ECI%20did%20not%20lift%20a%20small%20finger%2C%20despite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnavy-chief-yogi-adityanath-army-election-commission%5C%22%3Estrong%20protests%20by%20ex-servicemen%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20intriguing%20why%20the%20present%20ruling%20dispensation%20%E2%80%93%20with%20its%20massive%20propaganda%20machinery%20like%20a%20large%20political%20party%2C%20RSS%20and%20affiliate%20associations%2C%20IT%20Cell%20and%20a%20pliant%20media%20%E2%80%93%20should%20commandeer%20the%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20armed%20forces%20for%20the%20purpose.%20A%20question%20arises%3A%20Is%20there%20a%20credibility%20crisis%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20we%20call%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20gained%20independence%20one%20day%20before%20us%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%20state%E2%80%9D%20mainly%20because%20of%20its%20hijacking%20of%20the%20civil%20services%20and%20politicisation%20of%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Is%20India%20heading%20that%20way%3F%20As%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20brazen%20crony%20capitalism%20the%20country%20resembles%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%20state%E2%80%9D%20as%20defined%20by%20Robert%20Rothberg%20in%20the%20seminal%20book%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2Fj.ctt7scrg%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWhen%20States%20Fail%3A%20Causes%20and%20Consequences%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFailed%20states%20offer%20unparalleled%20economic%20opportunity-but%20only%20for%20a%20privileged%20few.%20Those%20around%20the%20ruler%20or%20ruling%20oligarchy%20grow%20richer%20while%20their%20less%20fortunate%20brethren%20starve%E2%80%A6%20The%20privilege%20of%20making%20real%20money%20when%20everything%20else%20is%20deteriorating%20is%20confined%20to%20clients%20of%20the%20ruling%20elite%E2%80%A6%20The%20nation-state%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20maximize%20the%20well-being%20and%20prosperity%20of%20all%20its%20citizens%20is%20conspicuously%20absent%2C%20if%20it%20ever%20existed%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommandeering%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20civil%20services%20and%20the%20armed%20forces%20for%20political%20propaganda%2C%20thereby%20severely%20denting%20their%20independence%20and%20integrity%2C%20will%20only%20hasten%20the%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fm-g-devasahayam-2%5C%22%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699010965000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154708%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.46.47-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-services-armed-forces-propaganda-india-failed-state%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'Rath%20Prabhari'%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence's%20'selfie-point'%20orders%20are%20obviously%20aimed%20at%20creating%20a%20positive%20public%20perception%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20general%20elections%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-services-armed-forces-propaganda-india-failed-state%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Xi%3A%20China-Germany%20cooperation%20has%20become%20more%20robust%2C%20solid%20and%20dynamic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699010752000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-