ran%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(disrobing)%20may%20sound%20like%20an%20excellent%20analogy%20%E2%80%93%20while%20being%20a%20deliberate%20nudge%20to%20potential%20news%20headlines%20%E2%80%93%20suggestive%20also%20of%20the%20sharpening%20divide%20between%20us%20versus%20them%2C%20before%20the%20upcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20there%20is%20more%20to%20it%20than%20meets%20the%20eye.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20changed%20since%20%3Cem%3EMahabharat%3C%2Fem%3E%20days%2C%20remarkably%20and%20concerningly%2C%20is%20the%20solitude%20of%20the%20woman%20in%20frame.%20While%20there%20was%20one%20Draupadi%20who%20garnered%20all%20the%20attention%20with%20other%20female%20characters%20essentially%20staying%20on%20the%20fringes%20as%20the%20Mahabharat%20unfolded%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20very%20different%20now%20%E2%80%93%20with%20Moitra%20doing%20all%20the%20batting%20and%20the%20fielding%20seemingly%20%E2%80%98alone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20some%20are%20calling%20her%20the%20%E2%80%98bengal%20tigress%E2%80%99%2C%20what%20lies%20hidden%20in%20the%20analogy%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20tigers%2C%20especially%20bengal%20tigers%2C%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalgeographic.com%2Fanimals%2Fmammals%2Ffacts%2Fbengal-tiger%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eknown%20to%20live%20alone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20So%20while%20TMC%20or%20other%20official%20parties%20haven%E2%80%99t%20come%20out%20openly%20in%20her%20support%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20for%20women%20all%20across%20India%20to%20show%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20Draupadi%20will%20not%20stand%20alone.%20That%20she%20will%20have%20the%20support%20of%20sisterhood%20and%20even%20brotherhood%20pouring%20in%20for%20her%2C%20across%20party%20lines%20and%20ideally%20across%20ideology%20lines%2C%20for%20isn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%98respect%20for%20women%E2%80%99%20the%20tagline%20of%20most%20political%20parties%20in%20one%20form%20or%20the%20other%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsking%20an%20MP%20about%20%E2%80%98who%20she%20calls%20late%20in%20the%20night%3F%E2%80%99%20or%20making%20innuendos%20about%20her%20character%20in%20an%20ethics%20committee%20discussion%20is%20absolutely%20abominable%20and%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20stand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20women%20playing%20a%20victim%20card%2C%20but%20simply%20a%20chance%20to%20address%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20and%20not%20just%20the%20tigress%20(pun%20intended).%20Women%20in%20politics%20in%20India%20have%20long%20been%20beaten%20with%20a%20characteristic%20%E2%80%98toolkit%E2%80%99%2C%20one%20that%20involves%20questioning%20their%20character%2C%20never%20their%20policies%3B%20branding%20her%20as%20too%20loud%20or%20aggressive%20or%20ambitious%3B%20questioning%20the%20personal%20choices%20she%20makes%20(what%20she%20wears%2C%20or%20who%20she%20dates%20etc.).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fparliamentary-ethics-committee-opposition-mps-mahua-moitra%5C%22%3EMahua%20Moitra%20Slams%20Ethics%20Committee%20Probe%20as%20%E2%80%98Filthy%2C%20Unethical%E2%80%99%2C%20Finds%20Support%20From%20Opposition%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20got%20to%20say%20enough!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20it%20should%20be%20said%20loud%20and%20clear%20by%20women%20%E2%80%93%20all%20women%2C%20who%20care%2C%20not%20just%20TMC%20women%20but%20also%20Congress%20women%20and%20BJP%20women%20and%20non-political%20or%20apolitical%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20in%20India%20need%20to%20proclaim%20that%20we%20cannot%20let%20women%20be%20taken%20down%20by%20shutting%20us%20up%20with%20a%20handbook%20that%20should%20ideally%20be%20a%20remnant%20of%20the%20past.%20We%20need%20to%20announce%20our%20own%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Manifesto%2C%20which%20needs%20to%20be%20hung%20on%20every%20door%2C%20every%20office%20wall%2C%20every%20twitter%20account%20and%20it%20can%20go%20like%20this.%20Repeat%20after%20me%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20be%20as%20bold%2C%20aggressive%20and%20ambitious%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20to%20be%20or%20not%20to%20be%20%E2%80%93%20someone%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20girlfriend%2C%20friend%3B%20fashionable%20or%20not%3B%20wear%20make%20up%20or%20not%3B%20be%20single%20or%20not%3B%20work%20or%20not%3B%20have%20babies%20or%20not%20%3B%20wear%20hijab%20or%20not%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20stay%20out%20late%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20for%20parties%20or%20for%20meetings%20or%20with%20friends%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20question%20%E2%80%93%20societal%20norms%2C%20governance%20policies%2C%20financial%20decisions%20(including%20Adani)%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20do%20all%20things%20otherwise%20legal%20for%20men%20%E2%80%93%20to%20pray%2C%20to%20follow%20their%20beliefs%2C%20to%20smoke%20or%20drink%20or%20break%20taboos%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20sit%20cross-legged%20or%20not%2C%20wear%20jeans%20or%20skirts%2C%20take%20last%20names%20or%20not%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20rise%20in%20pay%2C%20a%20rise%20in%20position%2C%20a%20share%20in%20property%2C%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20their%20due%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20do%20nothing%2C%20and%20stand%20aimlessly%20on%20roads%2C%20in%20parks%2C%20outside%20homes%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20the%20right%20to%20be%20noisy%2C%20to%20cry%20or%20laugh%2C%20to%20shout%20or%20to%20be%20silent%2C%20to%20have%20their%20privacy%20respected%20and%20do%20whatever%20they%20want%20in%20their%20private%20time%2C%20just%20as%20men%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWomen%20have%20a%20right%20to%20call%20out%20bullshit%2C%20wherever%20they%20see%20it%2C%20just%20like%20men%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20while%20calling%20for%20immediate%20implementation%20of%20the%20Women%20Reservation%20Act%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpriyankagandhi%2Fstatus%2F1713509000447479917%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20asked%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20why%20women%20are%20still%20slaves%2C%20and%20made%20a%20passionate%20appeal%20that%20we%20have%20to%20see%20ourselves%20beyond%20the%20repressive%20system%20that%20has%20been%20pressed%20upon%20us%20for%20generations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20cannot%20see%20more%20women%20be%20hanged%20by%20public%20opinion%2C%20through%20a%20distorted%2C%20vilified%2C%20systemic%20attack%20on%20them.%20Also%2C%20the%20time%20for%20mere%20tokenism%20on%20women%20issues%20is%20over.%20We%20have%20to%20let%20it%20be%20known%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.poetryfoundation.org%2Fpoems%2F46446%2Fstill-i-rise%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMaya%20Angelou%E2%80%99s%20inspiring%20words%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20we%20will%20rise%2C%20and%20that%20we%20shall%20rise%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20power%20to%20Mahua%20Moitra.%20Know%20that%20you%20are%20not%20alone!%20And%20for%20those%20of%20you%20reading%2C%20speak%20up.%20For%20today%20it%E2%80%99s%20her%2C%20tomorrow%20it%20will%20be%20one%20of%20us.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C