Ramadorai%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Kalakshetra%20Foundation%20in%20April%202023%2C%20recommended%20that%20able%20administrators%20with%20%E2%80%9Cbackground%20in%20human%20resources%20management%20and%20organisational%20skills%2C%20with%20a%20high%20level%20of%20interest%20in%20performing%20arts%20as%20additional%20interest%2C%20shall%20alone%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20the%20chief%20functionaries%2C%20such%20as%20Director%20and%20Principal%20of%20the%20Institution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESmt.%20Revathi%20Ramachandran%20has%20demitted%20the%20charge%20of%20Director%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkalakshetrafdn%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40kalakshetrafdn%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%2031%2C%202023.%20Shri%20Aneish%20Rajan%2C%20has%20taken%20over%20as%20Director%20(IC)%20from%20November%2001%2C%202023%2C%20with%20Kalakshetra%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Governing%20Board%20members%20and%20Advisor%20present%20during%20the%20occasion.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FioXCT9Jml5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FioXCT9Jml5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kalakshetra%20India%20(%40kalakshetrafdn)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkalakshetrafdn%2Fstatus%2F1720004710458171839%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EAniesh%20Rajan%20is%20a%20former%20Revenue%20Service%20Officer%20(IRS)%20who%20had%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20Kerala%20Customs%20Department%20Joint%20Commissioner%20before%20he%20became%20deputy%20secretary%20in%202022.%20His%20service%20as%20the%20joint%20commissioner%20was%20marred%20at%20the%20time%20by%20accusations%20of%20a%20political%20nature%20during%20the%20high-profile%20Thiruvananthapuram%20gold%20smuggling%20case%2C%20and%20Aneish%20was%20then%20transferred%20from%20Kochi%20to%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20protests%20in%20Kalakshetra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStudents%20of%20RDFCA%20had%20come%20forward%20with%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20against%20senior%20faculty%20Hari%20Padman%20and%20three%20members%20of%20the%20repertory%20%E2%80%94%20Sanjith%20Lal%2C%20Sai%20Krishnan%2C%20and%20Srinath.%20Following%20this%2C%20on%20March%2031%2C%20they%20staged%20a%20night-long%20protest%20demanding%20action%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EHari%20Padman%20was%20finally%20arrested%20on%20April%203%20after%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20him%20at%20the%20Adyar%20All%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Police%20Station%20(AWPS).%20He%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20in%20June.%20Meanwhile%2C%20no%20legal%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20so%20far%20against%20the%20other%20three%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%20of%20the%20student%20and%20public%20outcry%2C%20two%20survivors%20and%20six%20staff%20members%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20March%202023%2C%20detailing%20how%20the%20atmosphere%20at%20the%20Kalakshetra%20campus%20was%20toxic.%20The%20survivors%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Hari%20Padman%20would%20invite%20them%20to%20his%20residence%20within%20the%20campus%2C%20and%20denying%20his%20advances%20invited%20severe%20humiliation%20and%20repercussions%2C%20even%20leading%20to%20some%20women%20quitting%20their%20course%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStudents%20had%20also%20told%20TNM%20that%20their%20appeals%20for%20justice%20to%20Revathi%20Ramachandran%20had%20been%20dismissed%20outright%20or%20not%20given%20due%20importance.%20Moreover%2C%20students%20and%20faculty%20members%20have%20also%20said%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20on%20campus%20was%20casteist%20and%20misogynistic%20with%20women%20students%20constantly%20under%20the%20scanner.%20It%20also%20came%20to%20light%20that%20Revathi%20had%20allegedly%20covered%20up%20a%20mass%20outbreak%20of%20food%20poisoning%20on%20campus%20from%20the%20hostel%20food%20in%202021%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20When%20students%20became%20vocal%20about%20the%20attempted%20cover-up%2C%20they%20allegedly%20faced%20more%20retaliation%20from%20Revathi%20who%20accused%20them%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpainting%20her%20in%20a%20bad%20light.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20this%20year%2C%20a%20transwoman%20alumna%20of%20the%20RDCFA%20wrote%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20State%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Commission%20(SWC)%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fkalakshetra-alumna-alleges-sexual-assault-governing-board-member-writes-swc-176341%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elodging%20a%20complaint%20of%20sexual%20assault%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fins%3Eand%20transphobia%20against%20several%20Kalakshetra%20employees%20including%20current%20governing%20board%20member%20P.T.%20Narendran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20inquiry%20committee%20found%20Hari%20Padman%20guilty%20of%20gross%20misconduct%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20students%20who%20complained%20of%20sexual%20misbehaviour%20by%20Sanjith%20Lal%2C%20Saikrishna%2C%20and%20Srinath%2C%20be%20provided%20with%20legal%20assistance%20to%20file%20police%20complaints.%20The%20report%20further%20says%20that%20any%20sexual%20intent%20of%20the%20teacher%20to%20a%20student%20is%20an%20abhorrent%20expression%20of%20asymmetry%20of%20power.%20It%20also%20recommended%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20students%E2%80%99%20grievances%20redressal%20committee%2C%20as%20contemplated%20by%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20Regulations%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contents%20of%20the%20report%2C%20wh