ission%20in%20Rome%2C%20Italy%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20November%202%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20while%20terrorism%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunacceptable%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20solution%20had%20to%20be%20also%20found%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cproblems%20faced%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20initial%20reaction%20to%20October%207%20%E2%80%93%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20had%20only%20been%20to%20express%20%E2%80%9Csolidarity%20with%20Israel%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20Modi%20then%20reiterated%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20Israeli%20PM%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%201%2C400%20were%20killed%20by%20Hamas%20in%20a%20massive%20cross-border%20assault%20into%20southern%20Israel.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20Israel%20bombarded%20Gaza%20strip%20with%20massive%20airstrikes%2C%20which%20have%20killed%20upwards%20of%204%2C000%20people%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20are%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20weeks%20later%2C%20India%20reaffirmed%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20and%20the%20two-state%20solution%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20between%20Modi%20and%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20following%20the%20explosion%20at%20Al-Ahli%20hospital%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20did%20not%20back%20the%20resolution%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eabstained%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20the%20voting%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20that%20called%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20truce%20in%20the%20fighting%20to%20allow%20for%20essential%20supplies%20to%20reach%20besieged%20Gaza%20civilians.%20The%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20has%20now%20increased%20to%20over%209000%20in%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20countries%20outside%20the%20western%20bloc%20which%20has%20not%20used%20the%20term%20ceasefire%20or%20humanitarian%20pause%20for%20the%20current%20violence%20in%20West%20Asia.%20It%20has%20avoided%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98ceasefire%E2%80%99%2C%20while%20saying%20that%20the%20solution%20has%20to%20be%20found%20through%20negotiation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Jaishankar%20told%20Italian%20lawmakers%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20happened%20on%20October%207%20was%20a%20big%20act%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20taken%20the%20entire%20region%20into%20a%20different%20direction.%20But%20surely%2C%20it%20must%20be%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20hope%20that%20eventually%E2%80%A6the%20conflict%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20normal%20of%20the%20region%20and%20that%20it%20comes%20back%20to%20some%20stability%2C%20some%20cooperation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20as%20per%20news%20agency%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EANI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbalance%E2%80%9D%20has%20to%20be%20found%20between%20the%20two%20issues%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20issue%20of%20terrorism%2C%20and%20we%20all%20find%20terrorism%20unacceptable%2C%20we%20have%20to%20stand%20up.%20But%20there%20is%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20Palestine.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20solution%20for%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdialogue%20and%20negotiations%E2%80%9D%20are%20necessary%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20the%20current%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20view%20is%20that%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20If%20you%20have%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20you%20have%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20t