Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fponzi-scam-king-bernie-madoff-dies-behind-bars%2Fa-57206098%5C%22%3EBernard%20Madoff.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20crimes%20caught%20up%20to%20him.%20His%20crimes%20have%20been%20exposed%2C%E2%80%9D%20assistant%20US%20attorney%20Danielle%20Sassoon%20told%20the%20jury%20before%20they%20began%20deliberations.%20She%20added%20that%20Bankman-Fried%20turned%20his%20customers%E2%80%99%20accounts%20into%20his%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20piggy%20bank%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20up%20to%20%2414%20billion%20disappearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMark%20Cohen%2C%20Bankman-Fried%E2%80%99s%20attorney%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20they%20%E2%80%9Crespect%20the%20jury%E2%80%99s%20decision.%20But%20we%20are%20very%20disappointed%20with%20the%20result.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMr.%20Bankman-Fried%20maintains%20his%20innocence%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20vigorously%20fight%20the%20charges%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%C2%A0said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20else%20happened%20during%20the%20trial%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcryptocurrency-fraud-ftx-founder-sam-bankman-fried-on-trial%2Fa-66958423%5C%22%3EThe%20verdict%20came%20after%20a%20month-long%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20prosecutors%20argued%20the%20defendant%C2%A0had%20acted%20out%20of%20sheer%20greed%2C%20spending%20the%20money%20on%20investments%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20promotions%20for%20his%20cryptocurrency%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20court%20case%2C%20three%20of%20Bankman-Fried%E2%80%99s%20former%20top%20executives%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20fraud%20charges%20and%20testified%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20witness%20against%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20his%20on-again-off-again%20girlfriend%20Caroline%20Ellison%2C%20who%20told%20the%20jury%20that%20they%20had%20stolen%20%E2%80%9Caround%20%2414%20billion%E2%80%9D%20from%20clients%20of%20FTX%20before%20it%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20founder%20admitted%20to%20making%20%E2%80%9Ca%20number%20of%20small%20mistakes%20and%20a%20number%20of%20larger%20mistakes%E2%80%9D%20while%20running%20the%20now-bankrupt%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20mistake%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20failing%20to%20implement%20a%20dedicated%20risk%20management%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20that%20we%20might%20be%20able%20to%20build%20the%20best%20product%20on%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bankman-Fried%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20turned%20out%20basically%20the%20opposite%20of%20that.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20got%20hurt%2C%20customers%2C%20employees%2C%20and%20the%20company%20ended%20up%20in%20bankruptcy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20denied%20defrauding%20anyone%20or%20taking%20customers%E2%80%99%20funds.%20He%20had%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20all%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiggest%20crypto%20bust%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFTX%2C%20which%20had%20been%20among%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcryptocurrency%2Ft-64077796%5C%22%3Ecryptocurrency%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0exchanges%2C%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20protection%20on%20November%C2%A011%2C%202022%20in%20one%20of%C2%A0the%20highest-profile%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fftx-new-ceo-says-crypto-platforms-collapse-unprecedented%2Fa-63795258%5C%22%3Ecrypto%20blowups%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20traders%20pulled%20billions%C2%A0from%20the%20platform%20in%20a%20matter%20of%C2%A0three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20resigned%20as%20FTX%E2%80%99s%20chief%20executive%20officer%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20bankruptcy%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20interviews%20and%20public%20appearances%20in%20late%C2%A0November%20and%20December%20of%20last%20year%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20acknowledged%20risk%C2%A0management%20failures%20but%20said%20he%20did%20not%20commit%20fraud%20while%20r