ted%20for%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlthough%20Hamas%20seized%20control%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpalestinian-territories%2Ft-19099064%5C%22%3EGaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20in%202007%2C%20the%20PA%20has%20continued%20to%20pay%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20civil%20servants%20in%20the%20territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20PA%20is%20estimated%20to%20spend%20some%2030%25%20of%20its%20budget%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20it%20also%20provides%20funds%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%20medicine%20and%20social%20assistance%20programs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsraeli%20forces%20complete%20%E2%80%98encirclement%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%E2%80%99%20IDF%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20military%20says%20its%20troops%20have%20pushed%20further%20into%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccompleted%20the%20encirclement%20of%20Gaza%20City.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20added%20that%20the%20army%20had%20destroyed%20Hamas%20military%20installations%20and%20infrastructure%20as%20it%20advanced%20on%20Gaza%20City%20from%20several%20directions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20city%20has%20become%20the%20focus%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20to%20stamp%20out%20the%20Hamas%20militant%20Islamist%20group%2C%20which%20rules%20Gaza.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20estimated%20that%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20remain%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20besieged%20territory.%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20claimed%20that%20Hamas%20forces%20and%20military%20assets%20are%20embedded%20in%20civilian%20infrastructure.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHagari%20stressed%20that%C2%A0%3Ca