%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20see%20a%20Palestinian%20child%20%E2%80%A6%20pulled%20from%20the%20rubble%20of%20a%20collapsed%20building%2C%20that%20hits%20me%20in%20the%20gut%20as%20much%20as%20seeing%20a%20child%20in%20Israel%20or%20anywhere%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20Blinken%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20something%20that%20we%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20respond%20to%2C%20and%20we%20will.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20Blinken%E2%80%99s%20second%20trip%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20since%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%20has%20responded%20with%20a%20relentless%20bombing%20campaign%20and%20ground%20offensive%20in%20Hamas-ruled%20Gaza%2C%20which%20international%20aid%20organizations%20say%20is%20unleashing%20a%20humanitarian%20crisis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20has%20promised%20its%20full%20support%20to%20Israel%2C%20while%20at%20the%20same%20time%20calling%20for%20humanitarian%20%E2%80%9Cpauses%E2%80%9D%20to%20let%20through%20aid%20and%20allow%20evacuations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20explore%20the%20idea%20of%20as%20many%20pauses%20as%20might%20be%20necessary%20to%20continue%20to%20get%20aid%20out%20and%20to%20continue%20to%20work%20to%20get%20people%20out%20safely%2C%20including%20hostages%2C%E2%80%9D%20national%20security%20spokesperson%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20calls%20for%20pauses%2C%20however%2C%20differ%20from%20that%20of%20an%20overall%20cease-fire%2C%20which%20the%20US%20continues%20to%20oppose%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20only%20allow%20Hamas%20time%20to%20strengthen%20and%20regroup.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20Blinken%20is%20expected%20to%20meet%20with%20officials%20in%20Jordan.%20The%20Jordanian%20Foreign%20Ministr