%20especially%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20connectivity%20and%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20bus%20services.%20We%20have%20connected%20Dhaka%2C%20Shillong%2C%20Agartala%2C%20Guwahati%20and%20Kolkata.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20railway%20services.%20From%202020%2C%20we%20started%20container%20and%20parcel%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20Chittagong%20and%20the%20Mongla%20Port%2C%20we%20have%20connected%20the%20northeastern%20states%20of%20India.%20Our%20connectivity%20initiative%20worked%20as%20a%20lifeline%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20four%20new%20immigration%20check%20posts%20have%20been%20opened%20on%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border%20and%20our%20bilateral%20trade%20has%20nearly%20tripled.%20The%20journey%20of%20these%20nine%20years%20has%20made%20us%20reach%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Agartala%20Akhaura%20Railway%20Link%20and%20it%20is%20a%20historic%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3E'Firm%20Cooperation%20Between%20Countries'%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20said%20the%20relationship%20between%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%20is%20anchored%20in%20history%20culture%20language%20and%20both%20countries%20share%20values%20of%20secularism%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20countless%20other%20commonalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20Bangladesh%20attaches%20the%20highest%20importance%20to%20its%20relationship%20with%20India%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20connectivity%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20commerce.%20She%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%20for%20its%20significant%20contribution%20to%20these%20sectors%20and%20also%20extended%20Diwali%20greetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20joint%20inauguration%20of%20these%20projects%20manifests%20the%20firm%20friendship%20and%20collaboration%20between%20our%20two%20countries.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20you%20PM%20Modi%20for%20his%20warm%20hospitality%20during%20my%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi%20in%20September%202023%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20Leaders'%20Summit.%20I%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20for%20your%20commitment%20to%20strengthening%20the%20bonds%20of%20friendship%20between%20our%20two%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20for%20jointly%20producing%20the%20biopic%20on%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation%20of%20Bangladesh%20Bangabandhu%20'Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rehman%20-%20Mujib%3A%20The%20Making%20of%20a%20Nation'.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20extend%20my%20deep%20appreciation%20and%20thankfulness%20to%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20collaboration%20in%20the%20connectivity%20and%20power%20sector%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20our%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20the%20inauguration%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bangladesh%20ties%20are%20crucial%20for%20India's%20Act%20East%20Policy%20and%20these%20projects%20have%20also%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20more%20cooperation%20and%20opening%20of%20passenger%20and%20freight%20routes%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20and%20also%20for%20alternative%20supply%20routes%20for%20northeastern%20states%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698861420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fp68nao9o_modi-sheikh-hasina-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bangladesh-rail-link-agartala-akhuara-will-cut-short-agartala-kolkata-journey-pm-modi-sheikh-hasina-4536746%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20Bangladeshi%20counterpart%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20