t%3B%3A%20Suniel%20Shetty%20On%2070-Hour%20Workweek%20Suggestion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInfosys%20founder%20Narayana%20Murthy%20created%20a%20social%20media%20stir%20after%20suggesting%20that%20India's%20youngsters%20must%20work%20for%2070%20hours%20every%20week%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20boost%20the%20country's%20overall%20work%20productivity.%20His%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20national%20debate%20and%20invited%20both%20harsh%20criticism%20and%20voices%20of%20agreement.%20While%20some%20prominent%20business%20leaders%20backed%20Mr%20Muthy's%20workweek%20schedule%2C%20others%20on%20the%20internet%20slammed%20the%20billionaire%20and%20called%20his%20proposed%20work%20schedule%20inhumane.%20Now%2C%20actor%20and%20businessman%20Suniel%20Shetty%20has%20also%20shared%20his%20two%20cents%20on%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20LinkedIn%20Post%2C%20Mr%20Shetty%20said%20that%20the%20way%20he%20sees%20things%20when%20someone%20like%20Mr%20Murthy%20says%20something%20people%20should%20listen%20carefully%2C%20analyse%20it%20for%20themselves%2C%20and%20take%20the%20best%20out%20of%20it.%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20this%20is%20a%20contentious%20issue%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20stop%20%26amp%3B%20think%20about%20what%20he%20really%20meant.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20really%20isn't%20about%20the%20number%20of%20hours.%20It%20isn't%20about%2070%20or%20100%20hour%20weeks.%20The%20way%20I%20read%20his%20thoughts%20is%20simple%20-%20It's%20about%20going%20beyond%20your%20comfort%20zone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7125038777625976833%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221525%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Mr%20Shetty%20cited%20examples%20of%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20as%20individuals%20who%20excel