m%2C%20with%20the%20superstar%20being%20part%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20life-sized%20statue%20has%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%20World%20Cup%20clash%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20BCCI%20vice-president%20Rajeev%20Shukla%2C%20Mumbai%20Cricket%20Association%20(MCA)%20President%20Amol%20Kale%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20and%20Sachin's%20wife%20Anjali%20Tendulkar%2C%20daughter%20Sara%20Tendulkar%2C%20and%20brother%20Ajit%20Tendulkar%20were%20present%20during%20the%20unveiling%20of%20the%20statue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22de%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Statue%20of%20Cricket%20legend%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20unveiled%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGbeURccO7X%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGbeURccO7X%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FS0wRWttUnY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FS0wRWttUnY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1719693069019476426%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%201%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statue%20is%20dedicated%20to%2050%20years%20of%20Tendulkar's%20life%20and%20has%20been%20installed%20by%20the%20MCA%20near%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20Stand%20at%20the%20stadium%2C%20and%20it%20was%20unveiled%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudhir%20Kumar%20Chaudhary%2C%20team%20India's%20supporter%20and%20a%20fan%20of%20Sachin%2C%20was%20also%20present%20during%20the%20ceremony.%20He%20blew%20a%20conch%20shell%20and%20waved%20the%20Indian%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20greatest%20batter%20to%20have%20played%20the%20game.%20With%2034%2C357%20runs%20in%20664%20international%20appearances%20at%20an%20average%20of%2048.52%2C%20Sachin%20is%20the%20highest%20run-scorer%20in%20international%20cricket.%20He%20has%20scored%20100%20centuries%20and%20164%20half-centuries%2C%20most%20in%20international%20cricket.%20He%20is%20the%20only%20player%20to%20have%20a%20century%20of%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%2018%2C426%20runs%20in%20ODIs%20and%2015%2C921%20runs%20in%20Tests%2C%20Sachin%20also%20has%20the%20highest%20runs%20in%20both%20formats.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20player%20to%20hit%20an%20ODI%20double%20hundred%20and%20to%20have%20played%20200%20Test%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20has%20201%20international%20wickets%20to%20his%20name%2C%20making%20him%20a%20very%20useful%20part-time%20spin%20bowling%20option.%20With%20a%20total%20of%20664%20international%20appearances%2C%20he%20is%20the%20most-capped%20player%20of%20all%20time.%20He%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Team%20which%20won%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin%20has%20played%20six%20IPL%20seasons%20from%202008-2013%2C%20all%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20where%20he%20has%20scored%20a%20total%20of%202334%20runs%20in%2078%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2034.84.%20Sachin%20has%2013%20fifties%20and%20one%20hundred%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20hitting%2029%20sixes%20and%20295%20fours%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20119.82.%20He%20won%20the%202013%20edition%20of%20the%20tournament%20with%20the%20franchise%20as%20a%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin's%20best%20performance%20came%20in%20IPL%202010.%20He%20scored%20618%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2047.53%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20132.61.%20He%20scored%20five%20fifties%20that%20season%20and%20his%20best%20individual%20score%20was%2089*.%20He%20won%20the%20'Orange%20Cap'%20that%20season.%20MI%20finished%20as%20runners-up%20that%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhjl8ti4g_sachin-wc_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20life-sized%20statue%20has%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20clash%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A134%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMaratha%20Reservation%20Without%20Touching%20Existing%20Quotas%26quot%3B%3A%20Eknath%20Shinde%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20held%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%20decided%20that%20reservation%20should%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20without%20tampering%20with%20the%20existing%20quotas%20of%20other%20communities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20n%20Mumbai%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20also%20appealed%20activist%20Manoj%20J