0life%20skills%20education%20in%20India%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20empower%20individuals%20to%20acquire%20essential%20life%20skills%20through%20sports.%20By%20gathering%20on%20the%20playground%2C%20we%20especially%20empower%20girls%20to%20assert%20their%20presence%20in%20a%20domain%20traditionally%20reserved%20for%20boys.%20We%20aim%20to%20challenge%20gender%20stereotypes%2C%20encouraging%20girls%20to%20break%20barriers%20while%20fostering%20equal%20participation%20from%20boys%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayant%20Rastogi%2C%20Global%20CEO%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20shows%20that%20adolescents%20in%20its%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magicbus.org%2Fuploads%2Fpdf%2FMB_Impact%2520Report%252022-23.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20programmes%20improved%20their%20school%20regularity%20by%2021.8%25%2C%20a%2031%25%20increase%20in%20perceived%20self-efficacy%2C%20and%20a%2034.7%25%20boost%20in%20resilience.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20boys%20being%20given%20a%20proper%20coaching%20for%20Cricket.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333297%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchool%20boys%20are%20being%20given%20proper%20coaching%20for%20Cricket.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Baddi%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20place%20where%20Magic%20Bus%20has%20actively%20engaged%20since%202015%2C%20a%20significant%20milestone%20was%20reached%20in%20March%202021.%20The%20organisation%20introduced%20a%20sports%20programme%20exclusively%20tailored%20for%20girls.%20Divided%20into%20two%20distinct%20phases%20from%20December%202021%20to%20March%202023%2C%20this%20programme%20carries%20a%20primary%20objective%20of%20empowering%20girls%20aged%2011%20to%2018%20through%20the%20influence%20of%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Vivek%20Sharma%2C%20the%20programme%20manager%2C%2010%2C000%20girls%20were%20given%20sports%20sessions%20each%20in%20kabaddi%20or%20cricket.%20The%20girls%20also%20took%20part%20in%20tournaments%20within%20their%20schools.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20then%20chosen%20to%20compete%20in%20district%2C%20state%2C%20and%20national%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20objectives%20of%20the%20programme%20also%20include%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20the%20participants%2C%20which%20includes%20communication%2C%20socio-emotional%20learning%2C%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20says%20they%20were%20able%20to%20succeed%20in%20Baddi%20because%20Magic%20Bus%20had%20earned%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20trust%20first.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20planning%20since%202015.%20We%20worked%20with%20the%20girls%2C%20the%20boys%20and%20their%20parents%20and%20sensitised%20them%20%5Bto%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20girls%E2%80%99%20sports%20programme%5D.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20also%20actively%20addressed%20common%20concerns%20raised%20by%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F162218%2Fuber-cab-women-safety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregarding%20the%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20expenses%20of%20the%20girls%20participating%20in%20tournaments%20held%20in%20larger%20cities.%20Recognising%20these%20concerns%2C%20the%20programme%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20expenses%20and%20ensures%20their%20safety%20by%20arranging%20for%20accompanying%20coaches%20during%20their%20travel.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20the%20programme%20even%20covers%20medical%20expenses%20and%20provides%20first%20aid%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20way%2C%20we%20address%20any%20doubts%20community%20members%20may%20have%20about%20the%20program%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20questions%20are%20answered%20satisfactorily.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatthew%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20I%20played%20rugby%20with%20young%20people%2C%20I%20believed%20that%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs%20would%20lead%20to%20economic%20stability.%20However%2C%20we%20realised%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20a%20structured%20work%20environment.%20This%20setback%20inspired%20our%20%E2%80%9CChildhood%20to%20Livelihood%E2%80%9D%20programme.%20We%20understood%20that%20getting%20them%20jobs%20was%20only%20half%20the%20battle%3B%20keeping%20them%20employed%20required%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20right%20skills%20and%20guidance%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20grasp%20the%20value%20of%20work%2C%20learn%20skills%20beyond%20their%20chosen%20profession%2C%20and%20evolve%20into%20role%20models%2C%20actively%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20for%20their%20families%20and%20the%20entire%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20big%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation's%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skills'%20training%20to%20Indian%20kids%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20future.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F3_11zon-1698735055-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333300%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skills%20training%20to%20Indian%20kids%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20future.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Showed%20me%20the%20right%20path%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20points%20to%20the%20example%20of%20Prachi%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20had%20previously%20never%20left%20her%20village.%20Last%20year%20she%20travelled%20to%20a%20national%20athletic%20competition%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Bihar.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20parents%20were%20in%20complete%20shock%20that%20a%20girl%20who%20never%20left%20the%20home%20before%20has%20performed%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20had%20not%20tried%20with%20our%20child%2C%20she%20would%20never%20have%20reached%20this%20level.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20girl%20who%20has%20benefitted%20from%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20interventions%20is%2017-year-old%20Bittu%20Kumari.%20She%20joined%20the%20programme%20in%202017%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Class%208%20student%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20says%20she%20learned%20life%20skills%20through%20volleyball%20and%20kabaddi%20(volleyball%20has%20since%20been%20replaced%20with%20cricket).%20According%20to%20her%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20helped%20her%20make%20the%20optimum%20use%20of%20her%20talent%20as%20a%20kabaddi%20player.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20am%20a%20state-level%20kabaddi%20player%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20play%20at%20the%20national%20level%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20not%20found%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20I%20would%20not%20have%20made%20it%20this%20far.%20They%20showed%20me%20the%20right%20path.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20she%20has%20gone%20from%20being%20scared%20to%20speak%20to%20people%20to%20having%20the%20confidence%20to%20speak%20to%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CMagic%20Bus%20taught%20me%20communication%20skills%2C%20gave%20me%20confidence%2C%20taught%20me%20what%20is%20right%20and%20what%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20Magic%20Bus%20appointed%20Bittu%20as%20one%20of%20their%20community%20coordinators.%20While%20her%20ambition%20is%20to%20become%20an%20IPS%20officer%2C%20she%20also%20plans%20to%20play%20kabaddi%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20can.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20give%20me%20full%20support.%20They%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98When%20my%20daughter%20is%20on%20the%20right%20track%2C%20why%20would%20I%20stop%20her%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Matthew%2C%20these%20stories%20motivate%20him%20further.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20emotional%20aspect%20of%20our%20work%20reminds%20me%20of%20our%20mission%E2%80%99s%20importance%20and%20the%20need%20to%20stay%20rooted%20in%20the%20communities%20we%20serve.%20By%20understanding%20their%20struggles%20and%20empathising%20with%20their%20challenges%2C%20we%20ensure%20our%20programmes%20remain%20relevant%20and%20effective.%20This%20powerful%20motivation%20drives%20our%20commitment%20to%20doing%20right%20by%20them%20and%20striving%20for%20continuous%20improvement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20contributed%20by%20the%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698761468000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Using%20sports%20to%20teach%20crucial%20life%20skills%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20Foundation%20India%20is%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20impacting%204%2C00%2C000%20adolescent%20girls%20in%2022%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Made%20Of%20Shipping%20Containers%2C%20Our%20Home%20Harvests%20the%20Sun%2C%20the%20Rain%20%26amp%3B%20Kitchen%20Waste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHaving%20dedicated%20close%20to%2030%20years%20to%20talking%20about%20the%20environment%20and%20sustainability%2C%20Hyderabad-based%20M%20V%20Ramachandrudu%20wanted%20to%20lead%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle%20and%20be%20a%20responsible%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20finishing%20my%20studies%20in%201990%2C%20my%20work%20has%20revolved%20around%20environmental%20planning%20and%20implementing%20methods%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20advocate%20for%20water%20conservation%2C%20and%20encourage%20living%20life%20in%20greener%20ways.%20I%20have%20contributed%20to%20several%20non-profits%20across%20the%20country%20by%20talking%20about%20eco-friendly%20ways%20of%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20civil%20engineer%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20at%20a%20personal%20level%2C%20I%20always%20experienced%20a%20gap%20between%20preaching%20such%20practices%20and%20implementing%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20So%20when%20presented%20with%20the%20chance%20to%20materialise%20his%20vision%2C%20the%2057-year-old%20dedicated%20his%20efforts%20to%20building%20a%20home%20that%20embodied%20his%20principles%20of%20responsible%20citizenship%20and%20sustainable%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20in%202011%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20bought%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20and%20constructed%20a%20home%20spanning%202%2C700%20square%20feet.%20Within%20the%20open%20area%2C%20he%20cultivated%2040%20varieties%20of%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20including%20mango%2C%20orange%2C%20papaya%2C%20chikoo%2C%20banana%2C%20and%20jackfruit%2C%20as%20well%20as%2010%20types%20of%20hibiscus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%E2%80%99s%20noteworthy%20is%20that%20the%20entire%20structure%20is%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20materials%20like%20cycle%20rims%2C%20old%20glass%20doors%2C%20and%20shipping%20containers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-2-1698759550-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333369%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20entire%20structure%20is%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20materials%20like%20cycle%20rims%2C%20old%20glass%20doors%2C%20and%20shipping%20containers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20this%20house%20apart%20is%20the%20innovative%20construction%20techniques%20employed%20by%20him%20and%20his%20son%20Bharani.%20They%20implemented%20a%20range%20of%20eco-friendly%20practices%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20utilising%20greywater%20for%20gardening%2C%20producing%20shampoo%20from%20garden%20waste%2C%20and%20crafting%20the%20house%20from%20shipping%20containers%20and%20styrofoam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20father-son%20pair%20elaborate%20on%20the%20diverse%20methods%20they%20adopted%20to%20embrace%20an%20eco-friendly%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Our%20home%20is%20built%20using%20shipping%20containers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20striking%20feature%20of%20this%20home%20is%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20two-storey%20house%20spanning%20675%20square%20feet%20using%20shipping%20containers%2C%20adjacent%20to%20their%20main%20RCC%20residence.%20What%E2%80%99s%20noteworthy%20is%20that%20the%20entire%20structure%20is%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%2C%20the%20duo%20procured%20shipping%20containers%20from%20cargo%20companies%20and%20repurposed%20old%20steel%20pipes%2C%20typically%20employed%20in%20borewell%20excavation%2C%20as%20supporting%20columns%20for%20the%20containers.%20Additionally%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20shares%20their%20innovative%20use%20of%20broken%20ceramic%20pieces%2C%20transforming%20them%20into%20exquisite%20mosaic%20art%20for%20the%20bathroom%E2%80%99s%20flooring.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-1-1698759499.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20their%20new%20home%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20and%20Bharani%20embrace%20an%20eco-friendly%20lifestyle.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-1-1698759499.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-1-1698759499-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-1-1698759499-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-1-1698759499-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-1-1698759499-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20their%20new%20home%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20and%20Bharani%20embrace%20an%20eco-friendly%20lifestyle.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20container%20house%20boasts%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20a%20drawing%20room%2C%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20staircase.%20Also%2C%20they%20opted%20to%20use%20styrofoam%20as%20an%20effective%20insulating%20material%20for%20the%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Bharani%20has%20also%20made%20a%20shed%20from%20styrofoam.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20crushed%20styrofoam%20and%20mixed%20it%20with%20cement%20to%20make%20bricks.%20If%20the%20red%20brick%20weighs%203.3%20kg%2C%20the%20styrofoam%20one%20would%20weigh%20nearly%202.5%20kg.%20The%20advantage%20of%20using%20such%20bricks%20is%20that%20close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap%3B%20this%20saves%20top%20soil%20which%20is%20usually%20exploited%20during%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2029-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20join%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20initiative%2C%20Bharani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CYoungsters%20are%20still%20not%20completely%20aware%20of%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20sustainable%20living%20and%20mostly%20find%20themselves%20engrossed%20in%20a%20fast-paced%20lifestyle.%20Nonetheless%2C%20everyone%20should%20be%20encouraged%20to%20live%20a%20green%20life.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20free%20from%20the%20rat%20race%20and%20lead%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20individuals%20prefer%20eco-friendly%20homes%20to%20lower%20their%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20minimise%20energy%20usage%2C%20cut%20long-term%20costs%2C%20reduce%20waste%2C%20and%20promote%20healthier%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20can%20construct%20an%20eco-friendly%20home%20by%20first%20understanding%20the%20qualities%20of%20the%20scrap%20material%20used%20for%20construction%2C%20engaging%20in%20collaborative%20brainstorming%20sessions%20with%20skilled%20tradesmen%2C%20and%20cultivating%20a%20diverse%20capacity%20for%20design%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20also%20shares%20that%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20register%20their%20container%20home%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20ACs%20or%20coolers%20to%20regulate%20temperature%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2071-1050%2F14%2F21%2F14393%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESustainability%20Considerations%20of%20Green%20Buildings%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%202022%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20mentions%20that%20sustainable%20buildings%20can%20conserve%2040%20percent%20more%20energy%20compared%20with%20traditional%20buildings%2C%20increasing%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20decreasing%20carbon%20emissions.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20low-carbon%20materials%20in%20green%20buildings%20reduce%20lifecycle%20emissions%20of%20buildings%20by%20up%20to%2030%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20conserve%20energy%20in%20their%20unique%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244161%2Fthese-10-eco-friendly-homes-will-inspire-you-to-live-sustainably%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20father-son%20pair%20have%20employed%20an%20innovative%20masonry%20technique%2C%C2%A0the%20%E2%80%98Rat%20Trap%20Bond%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20popularised%20by%20renowned%20architect%20Laurie%20Baker%20for%20passive%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20traditional%20methods%2C%20this%20technique%20involves%20placing%20the%20bricks%20vertically%20rather%20than%20horizontally%2C%20aiding%20in%20temperature%20regulation%20and%20energy%20conservation%20within%20the%20structure.%20It%20creates%20a%20cavity%20in%20the%20walls%20and%20allows%20the%20thickness%20to%20remain%20the%20same%20as%20a%20conventional%20brick%20masonry%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cavity%20helps%20cut%20down%20the%20number%20of%20bricks%20and%20mortar%20used%20by%20up%20to%2030%20percent.%20This%20further%20reduces%20carbon%20footprints%20and%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramachandrudu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20container%20house%20boasts%20