Singh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20Singh%20has%20enjoyed%20coaching%20sports%20so%20much%20she%20got%20her%20E%20Level%20Coaching%20Certificate%20from%20AIFF%20(All%20India%20Football%20Federation)%20earlier%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20day%20I%20work%20hard%20in%20the%20office%2C%20but%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20there%20is%20this%20excitement%20that%20I%20must%20finish%20all%20my%20work%20by%205%3A30%20pm%20so%20that%20I%20can%20go%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20personal%20benefit%20for%20me%20from%20sports%20is%20that%20I%20sleep%20very%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDifficulty%20finding%20suitable%20spaces%20to%20play%20in%20is%20something%20Ruchi%20Upadhyay%2C%20another%20sports%20ally%2C%20also%20experiences%20in%20Varanasi%20district%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20love%20to%20have%20good%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20%E2%80%98good%20space%E2%80%99%20I%20mean%20level%20playing%20ground%2C%20no%20bumps%2C%20no%20pebbles%2C%20or%20stones%20or%20small%20bushes.%20And%20an%20ideal%20good%20space%20would%20be%20where%20we%20also%20have%20washrooms%20and%20drinking%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20lack%20of%20these%20spaces%2C%20the%20Varanasi%20programme%20has%2012%2C603%20girls%20and%20499%20sports%20allies.%20Upadhyay%20said%20she%20feels%20happiest%20when%20girls%20from%20her%20area%20qualify%20for%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FFOiqxTOVgAMt-ei_11zon-1698681080.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20girls%20participating%20in%20the%20sprint%20and%20run%20competition.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FFOiqxTOVgAMt-ei_11zon-1698681080.jpeg%201280w%2